004package data;
005
006/** Index-Value of an array of results. */
007public class Ival {
008  /** Index of results array. */
009  public final int ix;
010  /** Result value. */
011  public final int val;
012
013  /**
014  Constructor.
015  @param ix Index of results array.
016  @param val Result value.
017  */
018  public Ival (int ix, int val) {
019    this.ix = ix;
020    this.val = val;
021  }
022}
